title: Solitaire Classic Card
summary:
Classic Solitaire Game - Free and more addictive than ever!

Popular and free Solitaire game worldwide. A great way to relax and kill time, play anytime, anywhere with patience and perseverance. Get ready to challenge your wits and exercise your patience by testing the classic Solitaire game for free! Solitaire card game will surely satisfy you.

The task in this Solitaire card game is to move all the cards from the four decks - checkered, cue, spade and spade - to the drawer. In total, the classic Solitaire game uses a deck of 52 cards.

You need to arrange the cards in order from Ace to K (A, 2, 3 and so on). You can also move cards between columns and arrange them in descending order, alternating black and red. For example, you can only place a black 10 on a red 9. And only the King can be placed on an empty square. The whole deck can be moved by dragging them to another column.

The game Solitaire, also known as Patience in Europe (like England, France, etc.), is a single-player card game.
Solitaire Game - a fun selection from the Classic Solitaire collection, along with Cube, Freecell, Spider, Tri Peaks, Pyramind, Golf, Mahjong and Yukon.

Salient features:
- Classic, fun and engaging gameplay of Solitaire
- Mode for left- or right-handed people, providing a convenient experience
- 3 Challenge Modes, create more opportunities to experience the game
- Detailed statistics, help you track and improve your skills
- Unlimited hints and the ability to undo, help you take the steps with confidence.
